{"tid":2023850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普出口術行「負利率」 全球股市隨時陷大混亂","createTime":"2020-05-19T09:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T10:47:47.000Z","uid":118226,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6728f3b21499a0596fb96aff1657c313febc823e","tid":2023850,"uid":118226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:13:23.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普又亂出口術，向聯儲局施壓要實行負利率，聯儲局主席鮑威爾已即回應稱負利率政策根本不適合美國，並指已有各種工具來支持經濟。  日本及歐洲都曾實行過負利率刺激經濟，特朗普就認為聯儲局可仿傚相關政策，但鮑威爾指目前尚無明確證據證明負利率有效支持經濟，相反政策會扭曲金融體系，隨時引起全球股市樓市大動盪。聯儲局過去已多次在特朗普施壓下「跪低」，這次能否抵住壓力堅持原則呢？  今集【焦點燃論】請來吳明德（前美國銀行(亞洲)高級副總裁）、徐家健（美國克林信大學經濟系副教授），為大家解釋何謂負利率政策，以及拆解一旦美國實施負利率後，對世界金融體系的影響。<br />\n<br />\nsource：蘋果<br />\n<br />\n侵侵又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a323f2cff8bd98b11a152fa30fc43d8a29c54002","tid":2023850,"uid":118226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"侵侵又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f01ea387c6c05781abfa092a23c6f85d626755","tid":2023850,"uid":118226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連任機會睇黎"},{"pid":"90db85161215fd8f6d5ecd0b4af899d90e50fe2a","tid":2023850,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"吳明欽細佬咪即係大紀元時報<br />\n呢幾年唔見佢幫民主黨手"},{"pid":"e006dec1582f815ba8ac76eb8cb5d03a9b8c3